Welcome to Comerica Securities Online






 Comerica Securities Online provides you with an essential solution for managing your investments online. By utilizing this platform, you will be able to manage your financial portfolios in an efficient and user-friendly environment. This convenient service is at your fingertips day and night, seven days a week. 
When you manage your investments online with Comerica Securities Online, you have instant access to your balances, portfolio holdings, account activity, order status, cost-basis information, and more. Plus, you can view your brokerage account statements, tax statements, and trade confirmations online, reducing clutter in your mail box.

    This information is provided by your financial organization through Pershing LLC, member FINRA, NYSE, SIPC, a wholly owned subsidiary of The Bank of New York MellonCorporation.




